  "3330100": {
    "name": "圆滚滚！丑蛙池塘",
    "steam_appid": 3330100,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330100/extras/a048dcf33dce9216aa2abd6a2b7c398f.avif?t=1762853714\" width=616 height=65 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >布置你的专属池塘，摆放各种诱蛙装饰...然后，挂机等待！等待各种长相清奇的丑蛙们闻风而来，把它们抓进水桶里！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330100/extras/b487eee2e07e765dbd5f834cddebf274.poster.avif?t=1762853714\" width=616 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330100/extras/b487eee2e07e765dbd5f834cddebf274.webm?t=1762853714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330100/extras/b487eee2e07e765dbd5f834cddebf274.mp4?t=1762853714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330100/extras/75e4a2fde9bcb8a322be6db8ea6b9fab.avif?t=1762853714\" width=616 height=65 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >144只造型奇特的魔性丑蛙等你收集，每只丑蛙都有独特设计，奇葩又上头！你能集齐池塘里扭动的、蹦跶的、难以描述的“圆滚滚”全家福吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330100/extras/6ad1c35b9f837f47a62b3d5dac64b635.poster.avif?t=1762853714\" width=616 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330100/extras/6ad1c35b9f837f47a62b3d5dac64b635.webm?t=1762853714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330100/extras/6ad1c35b9f837f47a62b3d5dac64b635.mp4?t=1762853714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330100/extras/ed4ed94926f28cfafad27c88465b71dd.avif?t=1762853714\" width=616 height=65 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >把抓到的丑蛙放进养殖缸，装饰、喂食、悉心照料，把丑蛙养得圆滚滚、肉嘟嘟，然后再高价卖掉！赚来的钱可以购买池塘和养殖缸的装饰物，还有更多的丑蛙幼苗。至于丑蛙们是卖去哪里卖去干什么...就任君想象了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330100/extras/256a8a23a8a93f90783dd45b7e794dc5.poster.avif?t=1762853714\" width=616 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330100/extras/256a8a23a8a93f90783dd45b7e794dc5.webm?t=1762853714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330100/extras/256a8a23a8a93f90783dd45b7e794dc5.mp4?t=1762853714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还可以把养殖缸缩小到桌面的一角，让丑蛙成为你学习与工作的桌面伴侣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330100/extras/2db5137e04b0c8fec2b10a0ff90f6ad6.poster.avif?t=1762853714\" width=616 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330100/extras/2db5137e04b0c8fec2b10a0ff90f6ad6.webm?t=1762853714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330100/extras/2db5137e04b0c8fec2b10a0ff90f6ad6.mp4?t=1762853714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330100/extras/26c37b8469ddbe183cb1c1c4f604215d.avif?t=1762853714\" width=616 height=65 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >蛙灾可不是闹着玩的，偶尔也会有体形巨大的丑蛙来袭！快狂戳屏幕暴打反击，击败它们后可以获得特殊道具奖励或解锁稀有新丑蛙。随着游戏推进，还能获得隐藏信件，一步步揭开蛙灾背后的真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330100/extras/485ececd6f1ebbc3f25f4998985984b0.poster.avif?t=1762853714\" width=616 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330100/extras/485ececd6f1ebbc3f25f4998985984b0.webm?t=1762853714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330100/extras/485ececd6f1ebbc3f25f4998985984b0.mp4?t=1762853714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
